---
title: Cheddar Wonderburgers & OLD BAY® Fries with Caramelized Onion & Special Sauce
description: What puts the “wonder” in “wonderburger,” you ask? It’s all in the texture! To achieve crispy, craggy edges, we form ground beef into balls, then press down in a hot pan with a spatula to create super-thin patties. In the last few minutes of cooking, we top them with gooey white cheddar, then sandwich each between a potato bun with caramelized onion. A homemade special sauce is perfect for pairing with the Old Bay fries on the side—and will elicit major “oohs” and “ahhs” from your dining companions.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheddar-wonderburgers-old-bay-fries-28bb6d1d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/cheddar-wonderburgers-old-bay-fries-612648ae5c9d202ddd45ad9c-7046c9b0.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/cheddar-wonderburgers-old-bay-fries-612648ae5c9d202ddd45ad9c
author: Michelle Doll Olson
servings: 2
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
